#GRADING SYSTEM
names=["raM","RAJ","rose","JaCk","PaVi"]
marks=[[30,40,50],[66,77,55],[33,78,90],[87,97,57],[47,88,44]]
for i in range(5):
    average=sum(marks[i])//3
    if average>80:
        g= "S"
    elif average<40:
        g="Fail"
    elif average > 40 and average <50:
        g="D"
    else:
        g="A"
    print("{}.Mr/Ms {} has scored {}% - {} Grade".format(i+1,names[i].title(),average,g))

